{{#if (eq project.language "pt-BR")}}
# Gate de Documentacao — Regra #3

> **BLOQUEIO ABSOLUTO.** Sem docs por modulo em disco = sem implementacao.

## Checklist Pre-Implementacao

1. Classificar: feature nova ou bug fix/refactoring?
2. Se feature → identificar modulos afetados
3. Validar escopo (Regra #5): logica no projeto correto?
4. Verificar docs em `{{paths.docsRoot}}/{{paths.rules}}/{modulo}/{{paths.businessRules}}/{feature}.md`
5. Se NAO existem → `/plan-feature` ANTES de implementar
6. Se existem → usar como guia
{{#ifRule "tdd-enforcement"}}
7. TDD (Red): testes escritos e falhando? Se NAO → escrever ANTES
8. TDD (Green): so implementar apos testes existirem e falharem
{{/ifRule}}

## Estrutura de Docs por Feature

```
{{paths.docsRoot}}/{{paths.rules}}/{modulo}/
  {{paths.businessRules}}/{feature}.md
  {{paths.testPlans}}/{feature}.md
  {{paths.devPlans}}/{feature}.md
```

## Auto-Deteccao

**Trigga**: implementar, criar, adicionar, nova feature, novo modulo
**NAO trigga**: bug fix, refactoring, config, infra
**Na duvida → tratar como feature.**
{{else}}
# Documentation Gate — Rule #3

> **ABSOLUTE BLOCK.** No per-module docs on disk = no implementation.

## Pre-Implementation Checklist

1. Classify: new feature or bug fix/refactoring?
2. If feature → identify affected modules
3. Validate scope (Rule #5): logic in the correct project?
4. Check docs in `{{paths.docsRoot}}/{{paths.rules}}/{module}/{{paths.businessRules}}/{feature}.md`
5. If NOT present → `/plan-feature` BEFORE implementing
6. If present → use as guide
{{#ifRule "tdd-enforcement"}}
7. TDD (Red): tests written and failing? If NO → write BEFORE
8. TDD (Green): only implement after tests exist and fail
{{/ifRule}}

## Docs Structure per Feature

```
{{paths.docsRoot}}/{{paths.rules}}/{module}/
  {{paths.businessRules}}/{feature}.md
  {{paths.testPlans}}/{feature}.md
  {{paths.devPlans}}/{feature}.md
```

## Auto-Detection

**Triggers**: implement, create, add, new feature, new module
**Does NOT trigger**: bug fix, refactoring, config, infra
**When in doubt → treat as feature.**
{{/if}}
